<HEADLINE>
FT  10 OCT 94 / Company News This Week: Gardner Merchant - Other Companies
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The largest contract caterer in Europe announces its interim results on
Wednesday. However, a planned float appears unlikely until the spring. Last
April the group, bought from Forte for Pounds 402m in 1992, reported profits
Pounds 46.9m for the year to January 31 and turnover above Pounds 1bn.
</TEXT>
